  <title>Committing ink sketches using the controls ink commands</title>
  <purpose><div xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml" xmlns:my="http://schemas.microsoft.com/office/infopath/2003/myXSD/2006-02-10T23:25:53">This sample demonstrates how the Ink Sketch Commit options can be set and how the ink engine environment events are fired on either a desktop or Tablet PC. This sample is used in conjunction with the MapControl, ToolbarControl, and controls commands. </div></purpose>
